15\">BIM35015</a>, <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim35040\">BIM35040</a>, <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim35045\">BIM35045</a>, <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim35205\">BIM35205</a>, <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim35505\">BIM35505</a>, <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim35560\">BIM35560</a>, <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim35701\">BIM35701</a>, <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim35810\">BIM35810</a>, <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim35815\">BIM35815</a>, <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim35901\">BIM35901</a></p></td><td><p>43 TC 1</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"149\"><p>Broker’s commission</p></td><td width=\"149\"><p>Texas Land &amp; Mortgage Co v Holtham</p></td><td width=\"129\"><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim35580\">BIM35580</a></p></td><td><p>3 TC 255</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"149\"><p>Liabilities assumed on purchase of business</p></td><td width=\"149\"><p>The City of London Contract Corporation Ltd v Styles</p></td><td width=\"129\"><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim35655\">BIM35655</a></p></td><td><p>2 TC 239</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"149\"><p>Shares received for know-how</p></td><td width=\"149\"><p>Thomsons (Carron) Ltd v CIR</p></td><td width=\"129\"><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/business-income-manual/bim35720\">BIM35720</a></p></td><td><p>51 TC 506</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"149\"><p>Application of accountancy standards to leasing</p></td><td width=\"149\"><p>Threlfall v Jones Gallagher v Jones</p></td><td width=\"129\"><p><a href=\"https://ww